    EYEBROWS, EYELINER, OR LIPS, WE GOT YOU COVERED!

    Welcome to Red Carpet Luxury Spa: Elevating beauty with precision.

    At Red Carpet Luxury Spa, located at 197 Main St. Nanuet, NY, we proudly serve clients across Rockland County and Northern Bergen County, including Pearl River, Nanuet, Orangeburg, and nearby areas.

     

    Our permanent makeup services are perfect for busy professionals designed with you in mind, using gentle techniques, premium pigments, and clean, comfortable practices—you can relax and enjoy results that feel as good as they look.

    Meet your Cosmetic Tattooist!

    Hi, I'm Tzippora. I’m a licensed esthetician serving NY and NJ with over 6 years of experience. Specializing in eyeliner tattooing, My goal is to ensure that your permanent makeup perfectly reflects your vision. Every treatment is thoughtfully customized to suit your unique features and personal style. With hundreds of satisfied clients, I take pride in making the process seamless, comfortable, and beautifully tailored to you. From consultation to completion, your comfort is my top priority. I'll be with you every step of the way, ensuring you feel confident you made the right choice. 

    -Tzippora

    Is Permanent Makeup Right for Me?

    Permanent Makeup is for you if you:

    • Want to ditch the daily makeup routine.

    • Love a natural, polished look—without the effort.

    • Crave smudge-proof, waterproof beauty that lasts.

    • Have sensitivities or allergies to conventional cosmetics.

    • Need a low-maintenance way to feel confident every day.

    OUR PERMANENT MAKEUP GALLERY

    Powder Eyebrow Tattoo
    Powder brows create a soft, shaded eyebrow look that lasts 2-3 years, offering a more defined and filled-in appearance than microblading.
    Nano Eyebrow Tattoo
    Nano brows, a refined version of microblading, last 12-16 months with precise, natural-looking hair-like strokes.
    Lip Blush Tattoo
    Lip tattoo enhances the natural shape and color of your lips, giving them a fuller, more defined look with long-lasting results.
    Winged Eyeliner Tattoo
    Winged eyeliner adds bold definition with an outward, upward flick at the outer corner of the eye.
    Upper and Lower Eyeliner Tattoo
    Upper eyeliner tattoo defines the lash line, creating a fuller, more enhanced look with long-lasting, smudge-proof results.
    Dark Lip Tattoo Color Correction
    Dark lip tattoo color neutralization and correction enhance natural lip tones by balancing discoloration, providing a smoother, more even lip color.
